  "excerpt": "Living in a small apartment doesn't mean compromising on air quality. Discover proven strategies and products to keep your urban space fresh and odor-free.",
  "content": "<div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\">\n            <header class=\"mb-12 text-center\">\n              <div class=\"inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-[#E0EFC7] dark:bg-green-900/20 rounded-full text-[#FF3131] dark:text-green-300 font-medium text-sm mb-4\">\n                Urban Living Solutions\n              </div>\n              <h1 class=\"font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50\">\n                Best Litter for Apartments With No Ventilation: Small Space Solutions\n              </h1>\n              <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto\">\n                Living in a small apartment doesn't mean compromising on air quality. Discover proven strategies and products to keep your urban space fresh and odor-free.\n              </p>\n              <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 mt-6 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500\">\n                <span>Published February 1, 2024</span>\n                <span>â€¢</span>\n                <span>9 min read</span>\n              </div>\n            </header>\n\n            <div class=\"mb-12\">\n              <img src=\"/optimized/apartment-cat-lifestyle.webp\" alt=\"Small apartment living room with cat, showcasing space-efficient odor control\" class=\"w-full h-auto rounded-2xl shadow-xl\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" />\n              <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 text-center mt-2\">\n                Small apartments require smart odor control solutions\n              </p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-700 rounded-lg p-6 mb-12\">\n              <h2 class=\"font-heading text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-100 mb-4\">Small Apartment Quick Tips</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-200\">\n                <div>\n                  <strong>Best Location:</strong> Near ventilation, away from living areas\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                  <strong>Optimal Frequency:</strong> Daily maintenance, weekly deep clean\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                  <strong>Space-Saving:</strong> Compact, high-efficiency products\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                  <strong>Air Quality:</strong> Natural deodorizers + good ventilation\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\">\n              <h2 class=\"font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-6\">The Small Apartment Challenge</h2>\n\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-6\">\n                Urban cat owners face unique challenges when it comes to odor control. Limited space, poor ventilation, and close quarters with neighbors make finding the <strong>best cat litter odor remover for small apartments</strong> essential for comfortable living.\n              </p>\n\n              <div class=\"bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/20 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 dark:border-yellow-500 p-6 mb-8\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-heading text-lg font-bold text-yellow-900 dark:text-yellow-100 mb-3\">Urban Living Challenges</h3>\n                <ul class=\"text-yellow-800 dark:text-yellow-200 space-y-2\">\n                  <li>â€¢ Limited ventilation and air circulation</li>\n                  <li>â€¢ Shared walls with noise-sensitive neighbors</li>\n                  <li>â€¢ Restricted space for litter box placement</li>\n                  <li>â€¢ Higher humidity levels in compact spaces</li>\n                  <li>â€¢ Multiple pets in small areas</li>\n                </ul>\n              </div>\n\n              <h2 class=\"font-heading text-3xl font-b